N2  - A multivariate predictive model of organizational commitment explained a highly significant proportion of the variation in commitment within a combined heterogeneous sample. Subsequent analyses of the model?s generalizability indicated that certain nuisance variables did not significantly change the functional structure of the model or alter its ability to predict levels of commitment.
